OL,5,G2305 24 Hours in A&E
OL,6,     FA ten-week-old baby has choked on
OL,7,     Fhis milk. Tony has a flesh-eating
OL,8,     Fleg infection. And is the bruising
OL,9,     Fon Gerald's leg more serious than
OL,10,     Fhe realises?
OL,11,G0005 Emergency Helicopter Medics
OL,12,     FThe heli-medics race to help
OL,13,     FYvonne, who's in cardiac arrest.
OL,14,     FAnd in the Peaks, they land on top
OL,15,     Fof a steep ridge where Donna
OL,16,     Fcollapsed while out walking.
